      4:  'A year of home and roots. Family, property, a move or renovation, parents and inner security become the main theme. The focus shifts to your private space — you are settling your base.',
      5:  'A year of creativity and love. Romance, children, self-expression, pleasure, play and healthy risk. You want to shine and live in colour — a year to let your talent and your heart out.',
      6:  'A year of work and health. Job, routine, habits, body care and putting your affairs in order. A year of system and discipline — you build the rhythm that will carry you forward.',
      7:  'A year of relationships. Partnership, marriage, alliances and negotiation — much of this year is decided through a significant other. You learn to be in a pair and find balance.',
      8:  'A year of transformation. Crises and renewal, shared money, loans and investments, inheritance, depth and intimacy. Life changes at a deep level — you release the old to grow stronger.',
      9:  'A year of horizons. Travel, study, abroad, worldview, law and bigger meaning. You are drawn to expand your borders, outer and inner alike — a year of growth and faith.',
      10: 'A year of career and status. Goals, reputation, recognition and responsibility to the world. You are visible — a time to seek advancement and build a long strategy of success.',
      11: 'A year of goals and circle. Friends, teams, networking, dreams and plans, reform and kindred spirits. The future is built through community — who you walk with matters.',
      12: 'A year of endings and quiet. Solitude, rest, spirituality, inner work and release of the excess. A year to close a cycle, recover and prepare the ground for a new push after your birthday.',
